What is the total length of all the roads in San Francisco?


Assumptions:

  1)The questions concerns San Francisco's roads total length at present.

      Length of road = covering a distance equals to it's official stated length
      Roads are rectangular in shape
      Breaking down the problem: The answer depends upon below factors:

  2)Total area of San Francisco

      How much land constitute of total area
      Width of the road

  3)Solving each piece:

      Area of San Francisco= ~50 sq miles
      How much land constitute of total area = ~30%
      Width of the road= 40m
      Consolidating pieces: Land area= .3 * 50 sq miles= 15 sq miles Total length of all roads= 15 sq miles /40= .375 sq miles
